      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10"><p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🏆 CYCLIST</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">14 points · 7 letters · C(3)+Y(4)+C(3)+L(1)+I(1)+S(1)+T(1) · Bingo eligible</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10"><p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🏆 TYPIST</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">11 points · 6 letters · T(1)+Y(4)+P(3)+I(1)+S(1)+T(1) · Compact scorer</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">⭐ FLORIST</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">10 points · 7 letters · F(4)+L(1)+O(1)+R(1)+I(1)+S(1)+T(1) · Bingo eligible</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">⭐ CHEMIST</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">14 points · 7 letters · C(3)+H(4)+E(1)+M(3)+I(1)+S(1)+T(1) · H+C+M power</p></div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">-IST Suffix Strategy</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Back hook existing words:</span> If CYCLE, TYPE, or FLORA is on the board, adding -IST at the end creates a full word. You invest 3 cheap tiles to claim the entire word's score plus bonus letters.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Bingo-length sweet spot:</span> Many -IST words hit exactly 7 letters — CYCLIST, FLORIST, CHEMIST, BASSIST. These earn the 50-point bingo bonus. Hold I+S+T when you have a strong 4-letter base.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Pluralise with -S:</span> Every -IST word takes -S (CYCLISTS, TYPISTS, FLORISTS). This gives you flexibility — play -IST now, or hold for -ISTS if an extra S appears.</p></div>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">CYCLIST</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">14pts</span></span>
